NG0571:1239: ma lus gnas pa gzir zhing sgrol //
NG0571:1240: kyi ma ru ti sgra dang bkrag / gdug pa ma lus gnod du sngags //
NG0571:1241: las kyi dus su thun dbab 'phang *//
NG0571:1242: sku yi cho 'phrul rab tu dgyed //
NG0571:1243: 'bar ba 'jigs byed gtum sgra sgrog / 'jam dpal gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0571:1244: thun sngags kyi le'u ste nyer gcig pa'o //  // de nas 'jigs byed rgyal pos /
NG0571:1245: dgyes pa yongs su skong ba dang *//
NG0571:1246: gshin rje sku'i cha lugs ma lus rtags pa zhes bya ba la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0571:1247: rdo rje 'dzin pa rab tu byos //
NG0571:1248: yab gcig 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed mdzad lha //
NG0571:1249: gshin rje'i cha lugs shin tu 'jigs par ston //
NG0571:1250: gshin rje'i sku ni 'bar ba'i rgyal po ste //
NG0571:1251: shin tu 'jigs shing gtum rngam drag shul che /
NG0571:1252: khyod la bdag gi dad pas bstod cing mchod 'bul na //
NG0571:1253: bdag la khyod kyi yun du grogs mdzod cig khyod kyi thugs rje breng breng rgyun ma dgum //
NG0571:1254: thugs rje dad pa'i shugs kyis ma lus gshegs //
NG0571:1255: bcom ldan ya man ta ka sku yi cha lugs ni //
NG0571:1256: shin tu ngo mtshar gshin rje dpal la brjid /
NG0571:1257: khro rgyal dpa' brjid 'bar bas dgra bgegs 'dul //
NG0571:1258: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed ni grags pa'i brjid dang ldan //
NG0571:1259: ma mo ging la 'jam dpal dbang sgyur zhing *//
NG0571:1260: rtag tu lha mchog bdag la grogs mdzod cig / srin mo sha za stong ni bran du 'khol //
NG0571:1261: ging chen pho mo rnams ni bran dang g.yog tu 'khol //
NG0571:1262: klu rgyal pho mo rnams ni sku la rgyan du byas //
NG0571:1263: sha za gdug byed rnams kyis chas rnams dag par bstod //
NG0571:1264: dpal chen gsung gi gdug pa'i nga ro bsgrogs //
NG0571:1265: 'jam dpal sku yi thugs rjes bdag la dgongs //
NG0571:1266: bcom ldan 'jigs byed rgyal po'i sku stod cig khro mo yum dang chas te sku ston la //
NG0571:1267: g.yas nas yum bskyed e ke dza ti ma //
NG0571:1268: g.yon nas yum bskyed badzra pe ta li //
NG0571:1269: yum chen cha lugs khro rgyal sku dang mthun //
NG0571:1270: sku mdog mthing nag dbu gsum gdug pa'i dbu //
NG0571:1271: spyan dgu smin ma glog stong 'od du 'phro //
NG0571:1272: shangs dang zhal nas mi khrag rta khrag 'dzag / rno dbal mche ba dug gsum rtsa ba gcod //
NG0571:1273: phyag drug mi bzad gdug pa'i phyag mtshan bsnams //
NG0571:1274: zhabs drug brkyang bskum ma he'i steng du bgrad //
NG0571:1275: sku la 'phrin las rdzogs mdzad dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NG0571:1276: bskal pa me dpung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0571:1277: 'jigs pa'i nga ro'i sgra ni 'brug stong ldir //
NG0571:1278: sgrol byed gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0571:1279: gtum chen dregs pa thams cad 'joms pa'i lha //
NG0571:1280: dbang byed bdud 'dul dur khrod chas kyis brgyan /
NG0571:1281: khro rngam gdug pas srid gsum thal @#//
NG0571:1283: gtum chen rab 'bar gshin rje 'joms mdzad lha //
NG0571:1284: 'jigs byed ya ma ra dza'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0571:1285: nyi ma 'bum gyi 'od zer phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NG0571:1286: gdug byed mtshon cha mang po me dpung 'bar //
NG0571:1287: rab 'jigs gshin rje 'joms la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0571:1288: rdo rje'i sku la klu dbang rab brgyan nas //
NG0571:1289: dur khrod sha za'i pags rlon na bzar gsol //
NG0571:1290: sder chags sha za'i tshom bus thod du bcings /
NG0571:1291: khro bo'i rgyal po 'jigs byed hu~m sgra can //
NG0571:1292: zhal nas phat bsgrags khams gsum stong mdzad pa //
NG0571:1293: zhabs drug brkyang bskum brjid pas gshin rje mnan //
NG0571:1294: ljags 'dril tshems kyi gseb nas rdo rje thog chen 'bebs //
NG0571:1295: 'khor gyi ma mo mi bzad bran du 'khol //
NG0571:1296: tsham rngam drag po khro bo dkan gnyis brdabs pa yis //
NG0571:1297: gdug pa'i 'khor rnams 'dar lcug lcug / tshangs pa 'khor bcas rngul thigs phyogs bcur 'phro //
NG0571:1298: lha chen khyab 'jug ma ha de ba gnon //
NG0571:1299: phyag na b+han d+ha rlon pa rab bsnams shing *//
NG0571:1300: dngos grub 'khrug cing klad khrag zhal du gsol /
NG0571:1301: khyung dang 'ug pa lta bu'i khra bsnams shing *//
NG0571:1302: ma lus gdug pa dag la stong par mdzad //
NG0571:1303: gshin rje nag po ya ma ra dza khro bo 'bum gyi rje //
NG0571:1304: gtan gyi lhar yang khyod la gsol 'debs na /
NG0571:1305: khyod kyi thugs rjes rgyun du dgongs par mdzod /
NG0571:1306: khyung chen sngon po mkha' la lding ba bzhin /
NG0571:1307: khyod kyi sprul pa khye chung sngon po yis //
NG0571:1308: nad gtong srin mo'i tshogs rnams dbang bsdus la //
NG0571:1309: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig pa rdul du lhogs //
NG0571:1310: 'jigs byed de yi thugs dam rgyud bskul ba //
NG0571:1311: e ka dza ti gsang ba ral gcig ma //
NG0571:1312: mi 'pham khro gnyer g.yu yi ral pa can //
NG0571:1313: ral pa sprug pa'i skra gseb re re nas /
NG0571:1314: khro chung zhal gsum phyag drug stong khams 'gengs //
NG0571:1315: sku las sprul pa'i pho nyas stong gsum gang *//
NG0571:1316: kun kyang mi bzad ral gri lcags kyu can //
NG0571:1317: lcags kyus drangs nas dam nyams srog rtsa gcod //
NG0571:1318: bstan pa 'jig pa ma lus dbang du bsdus //
NG0571:1319: rnal 'byor mi bzad bstan la gnas //
NG0571:1320: rdo rje be con rab gnas te //
NG0571:1321: rgya mtsho gting du 'bru ba dang *//
NG0571:1322: ri rab rtse la bsnyag par bya //
NG0571:1323: 'jig rten khams su g.yab cing 'khrug / 'khor lo'i gzugs bri zor zhing 'phang *//
NG0571:1324: sku ni ting 'dzin zas kyi mchog / 'gu ru bla ma rab tu 'dud //
NG0571:1325: longs spyod zas dang 'du shes sgrol //
NG0571:1326: bsgrub dang rtags ni phrad mi bya //
NG0571:1327: ma lus gnas nas las su 'grub //
NG0571:1328: 'jig rten khams ni gzhal yas la //
NG0571:1329: ma he'i gdan bsam khro rgyal bskyed //
NG0571:1330: bzhengs dang spyan drangs mchod cing bstod //
NG0571:1331: de nas bsnyen bsgrub nan tur bya //
NG0571:1333: thugs rje bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o
NG0571:1334: // // de nas dpal khro mchog gsang bas chos
NG0571:1336: gsang ba po la bsgrag pa /
NG0571:1337: stong gsum 'khor lo bskor byas nas //
NG0571:1338: 'khor ba'i gzhi dang las kyi don //
NG0571:1340: gsang ba'i rgyud mchog dam pa 'di //
NG0571:1341: smig sgyu lta bur ming du btags //
NG0571:1342: mdo don rtogs nas rnal 'byor pas //
NG0571:1343: stong pa nyid dang snying rje dang *//
NG0571:1344: rgyu dang gzhal yas gdan khri dang *//
NG0571:1345: sku nyid yongs su rdzogs pa la //
NG0571:1346: phrag ni bcu gsum gnyis dang gsum //
NG0571:1347: lnga dang bdun dang gang yang rung *//
NG0571:1348: shes rab thabs su snang bar bshad //
NG0571:1349: gnyis med skyed dang ba ga yang *//
NG0571:1351: gsal byed sngags su rab tu sngags //
NG0571:1352: ting nge 'dzin dang sku ru rdzogs //
NG0571:1353: zhe sdang nga rgyal phrag dog 'phra //
NG0571:1354: gti mug dug lnga sku ru gyur /
NG0571:1355: khrag 'thung lnga yi ngo bor bshad //
NG0571:1356: rgyal ba sangs rgyas ma lus dang *//
NG0571:1357: bde gshegs gud na med par bshad //
NG0571:1358: 'gro dang srid pa sku ru snang *//
NG0571:1359: sku yi 'khor lo de dang yang *//
NG0571:1360: 'gro ba ma lus tha mi dad //
NG0571:1361: de dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NG0571:1362: cho ga lhag gam ma tshang yang *//
NG0571:1363: mi 'grub mi srid gdon mi za //
NG0571:1364: grangs su rdzogs na shin tu rdzogs //
NG0571:1365: sems nyid dag pa'i ngang nyid las //
NG0571:1366: sprul pa sna tshogs zad mi shes //
NG0571:1367: 'gro ba ma lus rang la snang *//
NG0571:1368: sku ru snang ba ma lus kun //
NG0571:1369: las 'phro dag tu snang du zad //
NG0571:1370: de bzhin nyid la 'gyur ba med //
NG0571:1371: sems can lta spyod mi mthun pas //
NG0571:1372: zhi bas 'dul ba'i skal med na /
NG0571:1373: khro bo dag tu sprul pa mdzad //
NG0571:1374: rnam rgyal gsang ba'i 'phrin las lung *//
NG0571:1376: kun rdzob tsam du bstan pa mtshar //
NG0571:1377: gso dang bdud rtsi'i bsgrub pa sngags //
NG0571:1378: srid pa'i rtse la rgyas par bya //
NG0571:1379: stab nas byung na sku la brgyan //
NG0571:1380: sems can las dang sbyin zhing sten //
NG0571:1381: dregs pa gdul bya rtan pa'i rgyud /
NG0571:1382: khro bya zhi ba'i ngang du bsdu //
NG0571:1385: ma lus 'dus pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NG0571:1386: rab tu 'dus so thig le che //
NG0571:1387: 'phrin las gang bsgrub gsang ba rgya //
NG0571:1388: gsang ba las kyi mthar gnas gang *//
NG0571:1389: rang gi bsam pa brtan por gnas //
NG0571:1391: gsang ba 'dus pa'i le'u ste nyer gsum pa'o //
NG0571:1392: // de nas yang dpal 'jigs byed kyi rgyal pos
NG0571:1393: / phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa la /
NG0571:1394: mi nub tsham rngam rgyud bshad de //
NG0571:1395: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba bshad //
NG0571:1396: rnal 'byor dbang phyug dam pa khyed //
NG0571:1397: gsang ba'i rgyud don dam pa 'di //
NG0571:1398: lnga brgya'i dus su gnas pa'i phyir //
NG0571:1399: gsung mchog yi ger snang nas kyang *//
NG0571:1400: tsit+ta gsang ba'i klong du chud //
NG0571:1401: sku dang theg pa kun la gnas //
NG0571:1403: de nas rab tu rtogs dam 'grub //
NG0571:1405: la gnas na phan du thogs //
NG0571:1406: de nas phyag na rdo rje la sogs pas mgrin gcig tu bstod pa //

NG0571:1413: gdug pa 'dul byed gsung sgra can //
NG0571:1414: ma lus dgra 'dul khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0571:1415: e ma byang sems rab tu gsang *//
NG0571:1416: rnam rtog rig pa chos nyid klong *//
NG0571:1417: stong gsum sprul pa khyod las sprul //
NG0571:1418: thugs kyi thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0571:1420: 'khor rang gi stan las langs te /
NG0571:1421: phyag na rdo rje'i rgyud don ma lus 'di //

NG0571:1423: skal ldan dbang phyug dag la gtad //
NG0571:1424: yid bzhin nor bu lta bur bcangs //
NG0571:1425: 'og min gnas su rab tu bsgrags //
NG0571:1426: rgyud dang 'bras bu rab bstan pa'i //
NG0571:1427: gdul bya rgyud du rab btul nas //
NG0571:1428: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du spros zab mo gsang ba'i rgyud mchog ste //
NG0571:1429: chos nyid rig pa'i klong nas phyung *//
NG0571:1430: 'khor lo bskor nas thugs su brgyud //
NG0571:1431: khros pa'i gshin rje rgyud du gnas //
NG0571:1432: sna tshogs 'byung ba'i thig le che //
NG0571:1433: ma ha su ka shri hu~m /
NG0571:1435: rtsa ba'i rgyud gtad pa dang */
